NzMxNTA0OTg0NjAyMHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "23_1777623111.774605", "card_id": "Q_2032055662855677948", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 24}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "综艺《我家那小子》吕严母子相处为何会令人感到钝疼？为什么吕严想要妈妈承认他受过委屈痛苦，但妈妈不承认？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "看《我家那小子》吕严和妈妈的片段，真的全程鼻酸。这不是狗血的家庭矛盾，而是无数东亚母子的真实写照：明明是最亲的人，却偏偏找不到最合适的相处方式。 \t 吕严的妈妈吕婕是一位非常独立的事业型女性，一个人把孩子养大。她的爱里带着严厉和控制，小时候没写完作业就把他赶出家门；许诺买电脑却空留箱子，多年后吕严提起，她却总是否认。这种 「 不承认 」 的相处模式，成了吕严心里的一根刺。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-01ef3e2f141514d23921c47346e8f0a9_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "65 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2032055662855677948"}}, "attached_info": "CkkI4uKw14qutrJIEAMaCTExOTI5ODA5OSCvqrvPBjAAOCtAF3ITMjAzMjA1NTY2Mjg1NTY3Nzk0OHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "24_1777623111.777618", "card_id": "Q_2032038624238228039", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 44}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "普通家庭家长很迷茫，小学三年级，要提前给孩子规划哪些未来必备技能？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "我家儿子目前是 3 年纪，作为江苏家长，我深刻的认识到孩子身上的学习压力很大，不断的刷题、内卷，我现在也会很焦虑，担心跟不上未来社会的发展速度。 也许未来十几年后的就业环境，AI 会带来颠覆性的改变，很多基础性的工作都会被替代。 想问问各位过来人： 1 、三年级作为一个关键时期，最应该培养哪些底层技能呢？ 2 、哪些技能是未来社会的刚需，我现在认为的是抗压能力、表达能力以及独立思考的能力。 3 、作为普通家庭，我是没有报高价兴趣班，所以在家落地可培养的方法有哪些呢？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-8ab1fbff40723db615528a4d42e5bcf4_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "61 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2032038624238228039"}}, "attached_info": "CkkI4uKw14qutrJIEAMaCTExOTI5NjYxMCDRirvPBjAAOFdAGHITMjAzMjAzODYyNDIzODIyODAzOXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "25_1777623111.778633", "card_id": "Q_2032742359033706287", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 28}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价原神月之六版本活动《礁与浪的相逢》？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-7797e50b3c5c82a9951587dd76086bb9_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "60 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2032742359033706287"}}, "attached_info": "CkkI4uKw14qutrJIEAMaCTExOTMyMDk5NCC4qcXPBjAAOBtAGXITMjAzMjc0MjM1OTAzMzcwNjI4N3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "26_1777623111.779415", "card_id": "Q_662345509", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 62}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么相声圈喜欢打嘴仗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "是为了流量吗？ 我都怀疑这次的对骂是剧本了。 越骂越有流量啊。 其实也是郭德纲的一个徒弟参与了后，才突然有的流量。 现在德云社这个话题，简直是流量井。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-b41a80078eff9669d84c137d316150ac_1440w.webp"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "58 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/662345509"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I4uKw14qutrJIEAMaCTEwOTQ2NTY4MCChj/y0BjAAOENAGnIJNjYyMzQ1NTA5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "27_1777623111.780314", "card_id": "Q_2033172301315667326", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 122}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待南开大学院长陈佺 Nature 子刊论文被「耿同学讲故事」实名举报数据造假？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "同济大学生科院院长团队顶刊论文深陷图片、数据造假风波尚未落幕，又一起重量级学术争议火速发酵！ 南开大学生科院院长陈佺领衔发表的 Nature 子刊《Nature Cancer》论文，被知名打假博主公开实名举报，直指论文图片异常、实验数据过度「完美」，存在刻意编造的低级学术不端嫌疑，且该研究依托国家基金委项目资助，舆论瞬间引爆科研圈。 本次学术质疑事件，全程发酵路径和此前同济顶刊疑云高度相似：论文先在国际学术同行评议平台 Pubpeer 被网友挂出疑点，作者仓促修正内容后，漏洞依旧明显，争议不但没有平息，反而持续扩散升级。 据打假博主「耿同学讲故事」爆料，此次涉事论文为《Targeted activation of ferroptosis in colorectal cancer via LGR4 targeting overcomes acquired drug resistance》。 核心致命疑点集中在实验数据层面：论文增补材料里，多组实验每组 64 组数据，小数点后两位数字高度雷同、完全一致。 面对全网质疑，论文作者在 Pubpeer 平台作出解释，辩称小数点后数字高度一致，仅是数据四舍五入导致，原始实验数据真实无误，不存在学术造假问题。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-b454d5c9068dcebf1954d1f95a1edb13_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "57 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2033172301315667326"}}, "attached_info": "CkoI4uKw14qutrJIEAMaCTExOTMzNzk1NyCjysvPBjAAOOgDQBtyEzIwMzMxNzIzMDEzMTU2NjczMjZ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "28_1777623111.781844", "card_id": "Q_324810843", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 79}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "「鸭屎香」是什么茶？为什么叫这个名字？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "凤凰单丛鸭屎香名字的由来？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-9764ba21ed4cdc86fcba3c0d905d0d12_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "55 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/324810843"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I4uKw14qutrJIEAMaCDM0NDU1ODA5II7j+eYFMAA43wFAHHIJMzI0ODEwODQzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "29_1777623111.783845", "card_id": "Q_2032401034061009163", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 144}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "员工厕所玩手机被开除，照片证据竟是门缝偷拍，以此为由解除劳动合同站得住脚吗？隐私权和工作纪律哪个优先？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "近日，一份由广东某科技集团有限公司落款盖章的《通告》显示，一名员工因长时间滞留厕所使用手机被扣除绩效 200 元并解除劳动合同。《通告》中展示了涉事员工在卫生间内使用手机的照片。 4 月 27 日，该公司法定代表人向九派新闻记者表示，《通告》内容属实，但公司没有在厕所装监控，相关图片是由公司管理人员发现涉事员工在厕所内玩手机后通过门缝拍摄而得。被处分的员工还处在试用期，经常找不到人。 针对网络上「公司在厕所装监控」等不实信息，其称公司行政部门员工已去派出所报警并备案。 内容来源员工在厕所长时间玩手机被开除，照片被通告展示，公司回应：厕所没装监控，管理人员发现后通过门缝拍的"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-a01a706f56ff9eb10fbfa4e72b49a74c.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "55 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2032401034061009163"}}, "attached_info": "CkoI4uKw14qutrJIEAMaCTExOTMwOTUyMyDWrcDPBjAAOMwCQB1yEzIwMzI0MDEwMzQwNjEwMDkxNjN4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}], "paging": {"is_end": true, "is_start": false, "next": "", "previous": "", "totals": 0}, "fresh_text": "热榜已更新", "display_num": 15, "display_first": true, "fb_bill_main_rise": 0, "head_zone": {"type": "billboard_lantern", "data": [{"id": "2033543178083644632", "link_url": "https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/2033518890710295058", "title": "日子滚烫，劳动至上", "source_type": 0, "attached_info": "Ci4QABoTMjAzMzU0MzE3ODA4MzY0NDYzMnITMjAzMzU0MzE3ODA4MzY0NDYzMngA", "tag": "关注", "tag_bg_color": "GRD01A"}, {"id": "1989780245977532317", "link_url": "https://www.zhihu.com/appview/community_construction", "title": "辟谣专区", "source_type": 0, "attached_info": "Ci4QABoTMTk4OTc4MDI0NTk3NzUzMjMxN3ITMTk4OTc4MDI0NTk3NzUzMjMxN3gA", "tag": "辟谣", "tag_bg_color": "GRD01A"}]}, "head_zones": [{"type": "billboard_lantern", "data": [{"id": "2033543178083644632", "link_url": "https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/2033518890710295058", "title": "日子滚烫，劳动至上", "source_type": 0, "attached_info": "Ci4QABoTMjAzMzU0MzE3ODA4MzY0NDYzMnITMjAzMzU0MzE3ODA4MzY0NDYzMngA", "tag": "关注", "tag_bg_color": "GRD01A"}, {"id": "1989780245977532317", "link_url": "https://www.zhihu.com/appview/community_construction", "title": "辟谣专区", "source_type": 0, "attached_info": "Ci4QABoTMTk4OTc4MDI0NTk3NzUzMjMxN3ITMTk4OTc4MDI0NTk3NzUzMjMxN3gA", "tag": "辟谣", "tag_bg_color": "GRD01A"}]}]}